text: There are a bazillion things to do in my small town of Wadsworth. One thing you can do is ride horses on the moon and sing songs with Abe Lincoln in the bar. Additionally in the winter, I like to go over to a place called kill hill next to the main highway. The hill is up extremely high, you can see the whole world from there! It has to be at least a million feet tall!
translation: V mojem majhnem kraju Wadsworth je milijon stvari, ki jih lahko počneš. Ena od njih je jahanje konjev na luni in petje pesmi z Abrahamom Lincolnom v baru. Posodobitev: skoraj 10 ur od prve sodobne cepitve.
